  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'You have proven yourself a vanquisher of bunnies and a killer of
      zombies.


      Your weapons and armor look well made.


      I think you
      are ready for active duty!'
    nextOption: Great!
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: "Our mission was to investigate a large force of Goblins in the
      area.  \n\nWe thought they were preparing for war against us.\n\nHowever, it
      seems they were just defending themselves from the undead."
    nextOption: These zombies are pretty grumpy...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'We... and by we I mean you...


      ...are going to take care
      of the undead threat.


      Once the undead are defeated, the Goblins will
      surely return home!'
    nextOption: That's a solid plan, what could possibly go wrong?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Report to Ser Invyncible to see how you can help.
    nextOption: Yes Sir
